00:00:00,090 --> 00:00:02,840
Be brave and make a secret gaming base under the bed. 

2
00:00:02,850 --> 00:00:05,240
Oliver's small bedroom had a regular layout

3
00:00:05,250 --> 00:00:07,480
just a bed and wardrobe with no privacy

4
00:00:07,490 --> 00:00:08,360
as a game lover,

5
00:00:08,370 --> 00:00:10,120
He often got scolded by his mom, 

6
00:00:10,130 --> 00:00:11,760
and there wasn't even room for a desk

7
00:00:11,770 --> 00:00:12,480
after getting fed up

8
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:14,870
He decided to kick everything out and start fresh. 

9
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:17,070
He welded a stepped bed frame against the wall

10
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:18,870
using galvanized square steel, 

11
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:20,790
covered it with eco-friendly wood veneers 

12
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,710
and added a big, comfy mattress

13
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,830
to make it bump proof. 

14
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:25,630
He added soft cushions on the sides. 

15
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,310
Under the bed, 

16
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,310
Oliver created a large corner wardrobe

17
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,630
to hang his stylish clothes

18
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,070
and store out of season bedding

19
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:33,710
with pull out baskets for shorts, pants, and socks.

20
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:36,160
A gauze curtain made it feel like a private dressing room

21
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:38,230
for safety, he added an iron guard rail

22
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:40,150
and a movable bookcase next to the bed

23
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:42,630
which connected to a suspended desk by the window, 

24
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:45,430
forming a study area with a small blackboard for planning. 

25
00:00:45,570 --> 00:00:49,200
the coolest part behind the bookcase was a secret gaming base with a computer desk

26
00:00:49,210 --> 00:00:52,600
a full set of e-sports gear and even a mini fridge under the desk, 

27
00:00:52,610 --> 00:00:56,360
he also added a perforated board for displaying his high end gaming equipment. 

28
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:59,830
Now Oliver can enjoy his gaming world without worrying about his mom catching him. 
